name: ABPropertyType
desc: These are the possible types of ABRecord properties.

items.name: var kABStringProperty: _ABPropertyType
items.desc: This property is an NSString object.

items.name: var kABIntegerProperty: _ABPropertyType
items.desc: This property is an NSNumber object representing an integer.

items.name: var kABRealProperty: _ABPropertyType
items.desc: This property is an NSNumber object representing a real number.

items.name: var kABDateProperty: _ABPropertyType
items.desc: This property is an NSDate object.

items.name: var kABArrayProperty: _ABPropertyType
items.desc: This property is an NSArray object.

items.name: var kABDictionaryProperty: _ABPropertyType
items.desc: This property is an NSDictionary object.

items.name: var kABDataProperty: _ABPropertyType
items.desc: This property is an NSData object.

items.name: var kABMultiStringProperty: _ABPropertyType
items.desc: This property is an ABMultiValue object containing NSString objects.

items.name: var kABMultiIntegerProperty: _ABPropertyType
items.desc: This property is an ABMultiValue object containing NSNumber objects representing integers.

items.name: var kABMultiRealProperty: _ABPropertyType
items.desc: This property is an ABMultiValue object containing NSNumber objects representing real numbers.

items.name: var kABMultiDateProperty: _ABPropertyType
items.desc: This property is an ABMultiValue object containing NSDate objects.

items.name: var kABMultiArrayProperty: _ABPropertyType
items.desc: This property is an ABMultiValue object containing NSArray objects.

items.name: var kABMultiDictionaryProperty: _ABPropertyType
items.desc: This property is an ABMultiValue object containing NSDictionary objects.

items.name: var kABMultiDataProperty: _ABPropertyType
items.desc: This property is an ABMultiValue object containing NSData objects.
